text.div:
This case-sensitive code system http://hl7.org/fhir/codesystem-properties-mode defines the following codes:

CodeDisplayDefinition
not-present Not PresentNone of the properties and filters defined by the code system are included in the code system resource.
partial PartialA subset of the code system properties and filter definitions are included in the code system resource.
complete CompleteAll the property and filters definitions for the code system are included in the code system resource.

name: CodeSystemPropertiesMode
title: code system properties mode code system

concept.definition: None of the properties and filters defined by the code system are included in the code system resource.

All the property and filters definitions for the code system are included in the code system resource.
